data.description: Comfort and convenience awaits you at Palm Villas II.  This home has been highly maintained and move-in ready! Open the front door and be greeted by the warmth of natural light and easily cool down with newly installed a/c units.  A private courtyard offers vibrant sunset views.  Two parking stalls are also included (1-open and 1-covered).  The amenities are nearby and waiting for you to enjoy!  VA Assumable Available @ 3.375%.  Call you Realtor for a tour today!
